    "| `lig` | `int` | ??? | Ligne de d\u00e9part |\n",
    "| `batterie` | `int` | ??? | Pleine \u00e0 la cr\u00e9ation |\n",
    "| `batterie_max` | `int` | ??? | Fourni en param\u00e8tre |\n",
    "| `survivant` | `str \u00f7 None` | ??? | Pas de survivant au d\u00e9part |\n",
    "| `bloque` | `int` | ??? | Libre au d\u00e9part |\n",
    "| `hors_service` | `bool` | ??? | Op\u00e9rationnel au d\u00e9part |"
